###############################################
ecommerce drop and drag cart
Pre 0.1 proof of concept
###############################################

This module extends the standard ecommerce module
giving you easy access to setting up a drop-and-drag
functionality for the cart.

This module is just one ideas at present, please dont
use it without thoroughly checking the code and dont try it
without a good understanding of ecommerce.

Any feedback or ideas appreciated


